metadata.name: SELF LOVE
metadata.description:
I love myself who continues to grow
I will never lose to my own weaknesses
I will never give in to the injustices of the world
My beauty is not superficial
If I can no longer grow, it's time to extinguish this flame. 


❤︎Character Profile❤︎

Name: Yang Wangwei (楊旺偉)
Age: ?
Theme Color: Red

Yang loves herself deeply, and her strong presence and beautiful red eyes leave a lasting impression on those who see her.
She lives to prove her strength to those around her, defeating anyone who is stronger than she is.
Yang is extremely assertive and refuses to curry favor with anyone or hold back her opinions, as doing so would be a disservice to her beloved self.
